&quot; Green Dragon Scales 250k PST &quot;<br>
The only way to fix the Severilious situation with having 21 guilds on the rotation ( and 5 more on the list to be added soon by the way ) is to make him spawn faster/ more often OR make the epic portion of Severilious a triggered version like they did the Undead bard/Trakanon for the bards.<br>
If things go the way they are currently, I personally think i will have more luck going to Veeshan's Peak to get My Green scale off of Hoshkar. All you warriors out there, get working on your Veeshan's Peak key quests and get your whole guild doing it. Think about it: Severilious drops the green scale 1 in 3 times on average. That is anywhere from 21 weeks <br>
( number of guilds on rotation ) to 63 weeks ( 21 x 3 attempts to ensure getting a scale ) to get a damn scale. I surmise that a whole guild of about 30-40 people could all get Veeshan's Peak Keys and get into Veeshans Peak to kill Hoshkar ( who reportedly always drops the green scale ) In the time period it would take to get a single green scale off of Sev.<br>
It boggles my mind that SoE don't see this bottleneck as being a problem.<br>
By the way Warriors, I have read  that SoE is possibly thinking of nerfing weapons with the effect of Taunting Blow or Enraging Blow because these weapons totally imbalance the taunt skill.<br>
personally, I cant taunt worth a damn without the effect I get from my Blade of Carnage. Nerfing the effect SoE? Watch me nerf my payments to you and delete my account.<br>
